---
// SearchHelp.astro - Component for displaying search help information
---

<div class="search-help bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200">
  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 flex items-center">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
    </svg>
    Search Tips
  </h3>

  <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
    <p>
      Our search supports several advanced operators to help you find exactly what you're looking for:
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-2">
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Exact Phrase Matching</h4>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-blue-700 font-mono">"cordless vacuum"</code>
          <span class="ml-3">Finds articles containing the exact phrase "cordless vacuum"</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Category Search</h4>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-blue-700 font-mono">category:cordless</code>
          <span class="ml-3">Finds articles in the "cordless" category</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Tag Search</h4>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-blue-700 font-mono">tag:dyson</code>
          <span class="ml-3">Finds articles tagged with "dyson"</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Author Search</h4>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-blue-700 font-mono">author:emma</code>
          <span class="ml-3">Finds articles written by authors whose name contains "emma"</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Combined Search</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-blue-700 font-mono">
            "battery life" tag:cordless category:upright
          </code>
          <span class="mt-1">Finds upright cordless vacuums with content about battery life</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-500 italic mt-4">
      You can use these operators in any combination to narrow down your search results.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
